name: Stock Maintenance Report
query:
select `tabStock Level`.`warehouse` as `Warehouse`,
`tabIMS Item`.`item_code` as `Item Code`, 
`tabIMS Item`.`item_name` as `Item Name`, 
`tabStock Level`.`qty` as `Quantity`
from `tabIMS Item`
join `tabStock Level` 
on `tabIMS Item`.`item_code` = `tabStock Level`.`parent`;
